node.text:
Available today on iTunes and On Demand!

Make sure to check it out 👀

Bran Marshall is a young man who has fled from Earth through The Gate to find a new home on Rhea. However, the early human settlers of Rhea have decided that they will no longer accept refugees from Earth, and Bran is forced to team up with a Rhean woman named Ohsha Rainer to stop her ship from killing thousands of Earth Refugees.

With: #caspervandien #johnrhysdavies @emilyhaigh8 @alanawallaceofficial @talagouveia @stephenmoyer  #glocmovie #ad

node.text: We’re thrilled to announce our support for this incredible project. The Definitive Retrospective Documentary on '80s Sci-Fi movies - In Search of Tomorrow - Kickstarter page is now online! Back now to be the first to receive the documentary, get your name in the credits, and receive exclusive rewards. Already 250% over its funding goal on the first day! Click the link in the bio for more info. Who’s in? ✋

node.title: In Search of Tomorrow - ‘80s Sci-Fi Documentary
